sections.title: Package supports Dart 2
sections.summary:
Package gets 20 points if its Dart sdk constraint allows Dart 2.

`pubspec.yaml` has no sdk constraint. Dart 2 support requires an sdk-constraint.
Add an sdk-constraint to `pubspec.yaml`. For example:
```
environment:
  sdk: '>=2.8.0 <3.0.0'
```
